// 🔍 SEE THIS → TRY THIS

// "Find pair that sums to X" → HashMap or Two Pointers (if sorted)
// "Longest/Shortest substring" → Sliding Window
// "All permutations/subsets" → Backtracking
// "Connected components" → BFS/DFS + visited set
// "Shortest path (unweighted)" → BFS
// "Top K elements" → Heap (PriorityQueue)
// "Sorted array + search" → Binary Search
// "Merge sorted things" → Two Pointers
// "Cycle in linked list" → Fast/Slow Pointers
// "Optimize brute force" → DP (if overlapping subproblems)
// "Tree level-by-level" → BFS with Queue
// "Process most recent first" → Stack
// "Range of values to search" → Binary Search on Answer
// "Frequency count" → HashMap
// "Unique elements only" → HashSet

